rows.label: tlk43100143_01_tlk0001
rows.name:
I hope I get to go up
that tower one day.

rows.label: tlk43100143_01_tlk0002
rows.name:
Maybe I can if I can become a Driver,
like my dad. Yeah, maybe if I
resonate with a Wind Blade...

rows.label: tlk43100143_01_tlk0003
rows.name:
But, I heard you also nead some
special skill called Leaping or
something...

rows.label: tlk43100143_01_tlk0004
rows.name:
I wonder if there's a Blade that can
do that... I'm sure I've never seen one
though!

rows.label: tlk43100143_01_tlk0005
rows.name:
Maybe if I resonate with a whole
bunch of Blades, I'll find one someday.

rows.label: tlk43100143_01_tlk0006
rows.name:
I bet I'd need a strong heart to get
myself a great Blade like that, though.
